                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8141" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1265</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3486 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ST新海金蝉脱壳失败--难逃退市危机</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">St Xinhai Gold escape shell failure-escape from the market crisis</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">孙思惟，陈业烨，林中原，戴文烨</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">苏州新海宜通信科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小微型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务舞弊；虚构收入；违规披露；退市</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Financial Fraud；Fictitious Income；Illegal Disclosure;Delisting</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ST新海是一家通信设备研发企业，2006 年11月首次公开发行股票并在深圳证券交易所上市，曾被认为是极具发展前景的优质企业。然而因为传统通信行业不景气，公司的发展逐渐偏离正轨，走上了一条不归路，直到2023年年初事件才完整的被曝出—公司收到证监会的《行政处罚及市场禁入事先告知书》，股票可能被实施重大违法的强制退市，ST新海从此走上了救市之路。本案例以ST新海在经营过程中的财务舞弊事件的前因后果为主线，详细介绍了企业的发展背景，财务舞弊的动机与手段以及造成了什么后果、应如何规避。旨在帮助学生了解上市公司财务舞弊的动因，识别舞弊的方法，以及学习相关的应对措施，为日后的实践提供相关的经验。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">St Xinhai is a telecom equipment r &amp; D Company, in November 2006, the initial public offering of shares and listed in the Shenzhen Stock Exchange, was considered to have great prospects for high-quality enterprises. However, because of the recession in the traditional communications industry, the company&#39;s development gradually deviated from the right track and embarked on a road of no return, it was not until the beginning of the 2023 year that the whole affair came to light -- the company received the SFC&#39;s “Notice of administrative penalty and prohibition of entry into the market”, and the shares may be subject to mandatory delisting for material offences, st New Sea has since embarked on the road to save the city. This case takes the causes and consequences of financial fraud in the course of St Xinhai&#39;s operation as the main line, and introduces the development background of the enterprise in detail, the motive and means of financial fraud, as well as the consequences of what should be avoided. The purpose is to help students understand the motivation of financial fraud in listed companies, identify the methods of fraud, and learn the relevant measures to deal with it, and provide relevant experience for future practice.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《审计理论与实务》、《财务会计理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CRIME五因素理论；财务舞弊的手段；公司治理与内部控制理论；财务舞弊带来的危害；财务舞弊的防范措施</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-02</td>
                            </tr>
